Maintainer: Shrikrishna Bhat K <skbhat.in@gmail.com>
Description: Silhouette diagnostics evaluate clustering quality by quantifying both cohesion within clusters and separation between clusters. This package implements advanced silhouette width computations for a variety of clustering structures, supporting: Simplified Medoid Silhouette <doi:10.1080/0094965031000136012>, PAC normalization methods <doi:10.1080/10618600.2022.2050249>, Fuzzy (soft) clustering and silhouette diagnostics using membership probabilities <doi:10.1016/j.fss.2006.07.006>, <doi:10.1080/23737484.2024.2408534>, Multi-way clustering extensions (e.g., biclustering, tensor clustering) <doi:org/10.1007/s00357-008-9005-9>. Computation and visualization <doi:10.1016/0377-0427(87)90125-7> tools are provided for robust, reproducible, and interpretable cluster diagnostics across standard, soft, and multi-way settings.
